Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自分の過去に囚われ迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:26.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:31.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自由に操れるかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}分からないよと　空は霞んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正解はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:42.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:46.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}忘れない記憶　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:52.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君を守り抜くと叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:57.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}離しはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:04.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:09.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}次への僕に　託したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:14.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:25.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:31.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}繋ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}无法摆脱自己过去的束缚  迷失了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:26.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}还自欺述说那并不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:31.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不知道这些是否能自由控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}天色为何又如此朦胧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}答案又在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:42.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}双手还残留着有什么很重要的事尚未完成的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:46.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这段记忆将尘封于心  永久保存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:52.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓要将你保护到底的决心已化作言语放声呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:57.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回放逝去的倒带  把对你永恒的挚爱捧在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}定不会轻易放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:04.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这是最后一次请求  将这散落一地的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:09.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}托付给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:14.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}曾经的约定  化作黎明的灯塔指引我前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:25.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我发誓将为了你支撑到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:31.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}连泪水也化作力量  一定会将心中描绘的所期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}与现实衔接
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:06.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:15.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:19.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:28.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:39.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:52.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:56.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:01.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:06.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:10.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:13.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:17.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:19.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.31,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.56,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.11,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:06.15,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:15.83,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}失准的时钟 记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:19.71,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.59,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:28.55,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你看 却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.85,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.10,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:39.18,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.23,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.73,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:52.57,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}让我忘却自己的过去 重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.78,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:56.87,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:01.29,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:06.88,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:10.51,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:13.93,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.97,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:17.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:19.64,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.81,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.23,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}与你携手迈进
